headline: West to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conferences
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services, Inc. (NYSE: WST), a global leader in innovative solutions for injectable drug administration, today announced that it will present at the Barclays 27th Annual Global Healthcare Conference on Wednesday, March 12, 2025 at 11:00 AM ET.
